data.description: A rare open builder lot with amazing views on the 11th hole at Wild Marsh Golf Course! this course is in the top 25 golf courses in the state. With approximately 1/3 acre corner lot, mature trees that is a good mix of species, this lot would be perfect to build the home of your dreams on, Imagine taking a short walk or with your cart and heading down the cart path to the Clubhouse for a round of golf, or just to go to the restaurant and enjoying a fantastic meal!
